<HL>
   Marketing &amp; Media:
   Norman Lear Aims
   To Scale Back Plans
   For Media Company
   ---
   ACT III Folds 2 Magazines;
   Sources Say Concern May
   Restructure, Sell Assets
   ----
   By Patrick M. Reilly and Richard Turner
   Staff Reporters of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
09/19/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B6
</SO>
<CO>
   AFP UNEWY
